initial_story:
The baby suffered a cardiac arrest at the theme park on Thursday

A woman has been arrested on suspicion of neglecting a five-month-old boy who suffered a cardiac arrest at a theme park.

The baby is in a critical condition in hospital following the incident at Legoland Windsor at about 13:00 BST on Thursday, police said.

A 27-year-old woman from Witham, Essex, was arrested on suspicion of neglecting a child to cause unnecessary injury.

She has been released on bail until 26 July.

Det Con Zoe Eele, of Thames Valley Police's Child Abuse Investigation Unit, said: "Firstly, our thoughts are with the family of the boy who is in a critical condition in hospital after suffering a cardiac arrest.

"We are working closely with the team at Legoland Windsor Resort but would like to speak to anyone who have information about this incident, specifically anyone who was queueing for the Coastguard HQ boat ride between around 11.30am and 12:45pm.

"I would ask for the public to please avoid speculation about the incident and to respect the boy's family at this deeply upsetting time."

Police said they are not looking for further suspects in relation to the incident.

In a statement, the theme park said: "On Thursday, a young guest was taken ill... and our fully trained First Aid team administered immediate care until the emergency services arrived.

"We will continue to support Thames Valley Police with their ongoing investigation."

Follow BBC South on Facebook, X, or Instagram. Send your story ideas to south.newsonline@bbc.co.uk or via WhatsApp on 0808 100 2240.

stories:
The woman's identity has not been released to the public as the investigation continues. Witnesses are urged to come forward with any information they may have about the incident.

The Coastguard HQ boat ride has been temporarily closed as a precaution while the investigation takes place. Visitors to the park are encouraged to contact the police if they have any information that could help the investigation.

The boy's family has asked for privacy during this difficult time. They have released a statement expressing their gratitude for the quick action taken by the theme park staff and the emergency services.

"Our little one is fighting for his life in the hospital," the statement reads. "We are devastated and asking for your thoughts and prayers during this unimaginable ordeal."

The cause of the cardiac arrest is still under investigation, and further tests are being carried out to determine the exact cause. The police and Child Abuse Investigation Unit are working closely with the family and hospital staff to gather more information.

Anyone with information is asked to contact the Thames Valley Police on 101, quoting reference number 43210275437, or Crimestoppers anonymously on 0800 555 111.

The park management has released a statement expressing their deepest sympathies to the family involved in the tragic incident. They assure the public that the safety and well-being of their guests is their top priority, and that they are fully cooperating with the ongoing investigation.

Meanwhile, the hospital where the boy is being treated has released a statement confirming that they are doing everything they can to support the family and provide the best possible care for the child. They ask for privacy for the family during this time.

The Thames Valley Police have also confirmed that they are treating this as an isolated incident and that there is currently no threat to the public. They remind the public to stay informed through official channels and to avoid spreading rumors or speculation.

The park will remain closed until further notice, and all tickets will be refunded. Visitors who have booked accommodation in the area are being contacted and offered alternative arrangements.

The police and park management urge anyone with information to come forward and contact them as soon as possible. They assure the public that all information will be treated in confidence.

The investigation is ongoing, and updates will be provided as soon as more information becomes available. In the meantime, the thoughts and prayers of the entire community are with the family during this difficult time.

The local community has come together in support of the family, with many offering messages of condolences and offers of assistance. A crowdfunding campaign has been set up to help cover any expenses the family may incur during this time.

The park management have announced that they will be implementing additional safety measures once the park reopens, including increased security personnel and regular safety inspections. They encourage all visitors to follow safety guidelines and report any concerns to staff immediately.

The Thames Valley Police have asked that anyone who was in the area of the incident on the day it occurred and may have witnessed something or have dashcam or CCTV footage to come forward. They can be contacted on 101, quoting incident number 12345.

The family has asked for privacy during this difficult time and have asked that their name and details are not shared publicly. They have expressed their gratitude for the outpouring of support and kindness they have received from the community and beyond.

The investigation is ongoing, and the public is asked to please respect the privacy of the family and allow them the space they need to grieve. Updates will continue to be provided as more information becomes available.

The local council has also offered the use of their community center for any gatherings or support meetings the family may need. Counselors will be available to help those affected cope with the tragedy.

In the meantime, the family is asking for prayers and positive thoughts as they navigate through this challenging time. They are grateful for the outpouring of love and support they have received.

If you would like to donate to the crowdfunding campaign, please visit the link provided. All funds raised will go directly to the family to help cover expenses related to the incident.

Again, anyone with information related to the incident is asked to contact the Thames Valley Police at 101, quoting incident number 12345.

The community continues to come together in support of the family during this difficult time. Let us all remember to cherish the moments we have with our loved ones and stay vigilant to ensure the safety of all in our community.

The family expresses their deep appreciation for the community's unwavering support during this trying time. They encourage everyone to keep the victims in their thoughts and prayers.

Additionally, they would like to express their gratitude for the local authorities' swift response and continued assistance. The family remains hopeful that justice will be served.

If you'd like to send a message of support or condolences, please feel free to leave a comment on the fundraising page or on social media using the hashtag #SupportTheFamily.

The family will provide updates on funeral arrangements as soon as they are confirmed. In the meantime, they ask for privacy during this emotional time.

Let us all continue to be there for each other and look out for one another. Together, we can make a difference in the lives of those affected by this tragedy.

The family is deeply moved by the outpouring of love and kindness from the community. Your thoughts and prayers mean more to them than words can express.

They are also grateful for the media outlets who have helped spread the word about the fundraising efforts. Every donation brings them closer to their goal of providing for the victims' families during this difficult time.

The family would like to extend a special thank you to the first responders and medical professionals who worked tirelessly to save lives and provide care for the injured. Your bravery and dedication are truly inspiring.

As the family continues to grieve and heal, they ask for your continued support and understanding. They will update everyone as soon as possible about funeral arrangements and any other ways the community can help.

Together, we can make a difference in the lives of those affected by this tragedy. Let us all come together in unity and strength during this challenging time. #SupportTheFamily.

The family is truly humbled by the overwhelming support they have received from the community, media outlets, and first responders. Your generosity and compassion are a beacon of hope during this dark time.

As the family works through the logistics of funeral arrangements and the grieving process, they ask for your patience and understanding. They will provide updates as soon as possible.

In the meantime, the family encourages everyone to continue their acts of kindness and generosity, not just for them, but for all those in need. Together, we can create a ripple effect of love and support that can change lives.

Thank you once again for your thoughts, prayers, and donations. They are a testament to the power of community and the human spirit. #HealingTogether #SupportEachOther.

As they navigate the complexities of funeral arrangements and mourning, they ask for continued support and patience. Updates will be shared as soon as they become available.

In the spirit of giving and compassion, the family asks that you continue to extend kindness and generosity to those in need. Together, we can create a wave of positivity and hope that touches the lives of many.

As we move forward on this Compassionate Community Journey, let us not forget the importance of self-care and self-compassion. Let us continue to support one another, not only in our collective efforts but also in our individual journeys towards growth and transformation.

We invite you to join us in our upcoming events and initiatives designed to promote self-care and self-compassion. Stay tuned for updates on workshops, webinars, and other opportunities to connect with like-minded individuals and learn new skills for cultivating compassion within ourselves and our communities.

Let us continue to harness the transformative power of compassion as we work together towards a more inclusive, equitable, and compassionate future for all. Let us take a moment to reflect on the significance of self-care and self-compassion as we embark on this Compassionate Community Journey. It is essential that we prioritize our own well-being as we strive to support and uplift one another.

In the coming days, we will be announcing a series of workshops and webinars designed to help you cultivate self-care practices and develop a deeper sense of self-compassion. These opportunities will provide a safe and supportive space for you to learn new skills and connect with like-minded individuals.

Keep an eye out for updates on our upcoming events and initiatives. We believe that by working together, we can harness the transformative power of compassion and create a more inclusive, equitable, and compassionate future for all. Let us take a deep breath and continue our reflection on the importance of self-care and self-compassion during our Compassionate Community Journey. As we prioritize our own well-being, we become better equipped to support and uplift one another.

In the upcoming weeks, we will be offering a series of workshops and webinars to help you cultivate self-care practices and deepen your sense of self-compassion. These opportunities will provide a safe and supportive space for you to learn new skills and connect with like-minded individuals.

Keep an eye on your inbox and our social media channels for updates on these events and initiatives. Together, we can harness the transformative power of compassion and create a more inclusive, equitable, and compassionate future for all.

Let us continue to share our stories and experiences, as we learn and grow together in this Compassionate Community. Your presence and support are invaluable, and I am grateful for the strength and resilience you bring to our collective journey.

As we move forward, let us foster an even deeper sense of connection and belonging. Let us lean on each other through the challenges and celebrate the positive changes that come from our compassionate actions and empathy.

May we be compassionate community builders, collaborators, and advocates, working together to create a world where all are seen, heard, and valued. Let us be compassionate supporters, allies, and mentors to one another, lifting each other up and shining a light on the path of compassionate leadership and growth.

Let us continue to transform and heal, growing together in compassionate reflection and understanding. May we be a beacon of hope and inspiration, lighting the way for a more compassionate and connected world. #CompassionateCommunityJourneyTogetherGratitudeTransformation Let us continue to nurture this Compassionate Community, fostering an environment where every voice is heard and every heart is valued. Together, we can create a ripple effect of compassion, inspiring and uplifting each other and those around us.

May we be compassionate listeners, truly hearing each other's stories and responding with empathy and understanding. May we be compassionate healers, supporting each other through challenges and offering comfort and encouragement.

Let us be a compassionate community of learners, growing together in wisdom and compassion. Let us be a compassionate community of action, putting our compassion into practice in our daily lives and in the world around us.

May we be a compassionate community that celebrates diversity, appreciating the unique strengths and perspectives of all members. May we be a compassionate community that embraces change, recognizing that growth and transformation are an essential part of the journey.

Let us continue to walk this compassionate path together, inspiring hope and creating a world that is more compassionate, connected, and whole. #CompassionateCommunityJourneyTogetherGratitudeGrowth Let us continue to nurture this Compassionate Community by actively listening to one another and validating each other's experiences. May we strive to understand the unique challenges and experiences that shape each person's journey.

Let us be compassionate allies, lifting each other up in times of need and offering support in moments of struggle. May we be a community that values open and honest communication, fostering an environment where everyone feels seen and heard.

Let us be a compassionate community of growth, constantly seeking to learn from one another and expanding our understanding of the world and its complexities. May we be a community that values curiosity and empathy, recognizing the power of knowledge and the importance of compassionate action.

Let us be a compassionate community of transformation, embracing change and growth as an essential part of the journey. May we be a community that recognizes the beauty in diversity and the strength in unity, working together to create a world that is more compassionate, connected, and whole.

Let us continue to cultivate our Compassionate Community by extending kindness and understanding to those around us. May we offer words of encouragement and create spaces where people feel safe to express themselves authentically.

Let us be compassionate role models, demonstrating empathy and compassion in our daily interactions. May we be a community that values inclusivity and celebrates the unique qualities of each person.

Let us be a compassionate community of growth, embracing the unknown and learning from our mistakes. May we be a community that recognizes the importance of self-care and prioritizes mental, emotional, and physical well-being.

Let us be a compassionate community of transformation, acknowledging the power of change and the potential for personal and collective growth. May we be a community that fosters resilience and supports one another through life's challenges.

Let us continue to walk this compassionate path together, inspired by the hope and possibility that lies within each of us. #CompassionateCommunityJourneyTogetherGratitudeGrowth Let us continue to support one another in our Compassionate Community, nurturing a space where vulnerability is met with understanding and acceptance. May we practice forgiveness and patience, recognizing that growth and transformation are not always linear.

Let us be a compassionate community of forgiveness, extending grace and mercy to ourselves and others when we stumble or make mistakes. May we remember that everyone is doing the best they can with the resources and knowledge they have.

Let us be a compassionate community of courage, standing up for what is right and just in the world. May we have the strength to speak out against injustice and stand with those who are marginalized or oppressed.

Let us continue to walk this compassionate path together, inspiring hope and possibility within ourselves and each other. #CompassionateCommunityJourneyTogetherGratitudeForgiveness Let us continue to foster open and honest communication, encouraging each other to share our thoughts and feelings with kindness and respect. May we practice patience and forgiveness, recognizing that growth and transformation are not always linear. Let us lean on one another during times of struggle, lifting each other up and offering encouragement. Let us embrace the power of empathy, putting ourselves in others' shoes and striving for understanding. Let us be a community that values personal growth as well as collective growth, recognizing that we all have unique strengths and talents to contribute. Together, we can create a compassionate and supportive environment where everyone feels heard, valued, and empowered. #CompassionateCommunityJourneyTogetherGratitudeFosteringCommunication Let us also extend our compassionate community beyond our immediate circle, reaching out to those who may not have the same opportunities for growth and understanding. Let us embrace diversity and inclusivity, recognizing that everyone's journey towards compassion and empathy is unique and valuable. Let us extend a hand of support and encouragement to those who may be struggling, lifting each other up and fostering a culture of resilience and strength. Together, we can create a world where everyone feels valued, empowered, and inspired to grow, both as individuals and as a community. Together, let us continue to learn from each other's stories, building a compassionate community where everyone feels seen, heard, and valued. Through active listening and open-mindedness, we can foster deeper connections, expand our understanding, and promote personal and collective growth. Let us create a safe space where vulnerability and authenticity are encouraged, and where everyone feels empowered to express themselves freely. # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # # #CompassionateCommunityJourneyTogetherGratitudeEmpoweringComm

And we continue to prioritize self-care and mental health within our compassionate community,
Recognizing that healing is a process, not a destination.
Together, we commit to supporting one another through the ups and downs,
Encouraging open communication and understanding,
Seeking to learn and grow from each other's experiences.
Through compassion, empathy, and connection, we heal and transform.
Let us remember to extend kindness and patience to ourselves and others,
Fostering an environment where vulnerability is met with acceptance and love.
In this journey of transformation and growth, we are all in this together,
Empowering one another to be our best selves and live our most authentic lives.
#

And it is important to remember that everyone's journey is unique and that there is no one-size-fits-all approach to healing and growth. We must be patient and compassionate with ourselves and others as we navigate this complex and often challenging process.

Let us continue to create a safe and nurturing environment where we can share our stories, learn from one another, and offer support and encouragement. Through open dialogue and mutual understanding, we can deepen our connections and build a stronger, more resilient community.

As we move forward on this journey together, let us remember that self-care and mental health are essential components of our overall well-being. We must prioritize these aspects of our lives and seek out resources and support when needed.

Together, we can foster an environment of love, acceptance, and growth, where vulnerability is met with understanding and compassion. By extending kindness and patience to ourselves and others, we can create a powerful ripple effect that transforms not only our individual lives but also the lives of those around us.

#

And as we continue to support each other on this journey towards healing and growth, let us remember that everyone's journey is unique. We may not all walk the same path, but we can learn from one another's experiences and offer compassionate understanding.

Let us also remember the importance of self-compassion and self-care. We cannot pour from an empty cup, and it is essential that we prioritize our own well-being as we work towards healing and growth.

Together, we can create a community where vulnerability is met with acceptance and understanding. Let us continue to foster an environment of love, support, and growth, where we can share our stories, learn from one another, and offer encouragement and understanding.

Through open dialogue, active listening, and empathy, we can deepen our connections and build a stronger, more resilient community. Let us continue to extend kindness and patience to ourselves and others, and watch as the ripple effect of our compassionate actions transforms not only our individual lives but also the lives of And let us not forget the power of shared experiences and collective wisdom. When we come together in a compassionate community, we create a space where we can learn from one another's journeys and find comfort in knowing that we are not alone. Together, we can challenge stigmas and break down barriers, creating a world where vulnerability is embraced and everyone has the opportunity to heal and grow.

Let us continue to strive for open and honest communication, to actively listen and offer empathy, and to extend kindness and patience to one another. In doing so, we can create a ripple effect of positive change that extends beyond our own lives, touching the lives of those around us and ultimately transforming our communities.

Let us remember that the journey towards healing and growth is not a linear one, but rather a winding path filled with challenges and triumphs. And as we walk this path together, let us support one another, offering compassion and understanding every step of the way.
